cenes at Prince Edward metro station, which saw terrified bystanders caught up in the melee, fell far short of international policing standards.}}</ref>\n\n<ref name=\"ap_20190824_36arrested\">{{cite web |last1=Chan |first1=Kelvin |last2=Cheung |first2=Kin |title=Hong Kong police draw guns, arrest 36 from latest protest |url=https://apnews.com/b116e37159164abb9bfede0bc341dd0a |agency=[[Associated Press]] |accessdate=31 August 2019 |date=24 August 2019}}</ref>\n\n<ref name=\"ap_20191105_knifearrest\">{{cite news |last1=Ng |first1=Eileen |title=Hong Kong police arrest man in knife attack at protest site |url=https://apnews.com/fea5339c6b414b82a7df89331e5800ee |accessdate=5 November 2019 |agency=[[Associated Press]] |date=5 November 2019}}</ref>\n\n<ref name=\"appledaily_20736871\">{{cite web|url=https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/daily/article/20190725/20736871 |script-title=zh:\u5143\u6717\u6050\u8972 ICAC\u67e5\u8b66\u9ed1\u52fe\u7d50 \u524d\u8abf\u67e5\u54e1\uff1a\u5018\u8896\u624b\u65c1\u89c0 \u8b66\u968a\u4e0a\u4e0b\u7686\u7006\u8077|website=Apple Daily |language=zh|accessdate=25 July 2019}}</ref>\n\n<ref name=\"appledaily_59771130\">{{cite news|language=zh-hk |script-title=zh:\u7c89\u5dba21\u6b72\u5927\u5b78\u751f\u7559\u300c\u53cd\u9001\u4e2d\u300d\u5b57\u53e5\u5f8c\u58ae\u6a13\u4ea1|url=https://hk.news.appledaily.com/breaking/realtime/article/20190629/59771130|work=Apple Daily |location=Hong Kong|accessdate=29 June 2019}}</ref>\n\n<ref name=\"appledaily_59773700\">{{cite web|url=https://hk.news.appledaily.com/breaking/realtime/article/20190630/59773700 |script-title=zh:\u3010\u5f15\u6e21\u60e1\u6cd5\u301129\u6b72\u5973\u5b50\u4e2d\u74b0ifc\u58ae\u6a13\u4ea1 fb\u7559\u907a\u8a00\uff1a\u4e03\u4e00\u6211\u53bb\u4e0d\u4e86|date=30 June 2019|website=Apple Daily |language=zh|url-status=|accessdate=30 June 2019}}</ref>\n\n<ref name=\"appledaily_59774211\">{{cite web|url=https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/realtime/article/20190701/59774211 |script-title=zh:\u30107